Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}卢纳帝国 边境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算周边被破坏也不要紧的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬头会被敌人发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卢纳的魔法骑士团

Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德 城下町
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据今晨发布的敕令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王派的贵族们一齐高升
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的英雄王席恩·阿斯塔尔陛下的改革可不仅限于此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们市民
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有能力就能获得官职
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为已经搞定了国王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他居然出这招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区下贱的狗杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢耍弄我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下也真够狠的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 从少将升到元帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一下升了多少阶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么成元帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元帅还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 再上去只有名誉元帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁跟你说这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样靠你的关系升官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们会很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这形势下采取这样的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否略有些欠思虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 这在反国王派贵族看来根本就是挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是摆明了在说“有意见就放马过来吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们升官竟然还有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真是清心寡欲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等追随陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未想过功名利禄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是受陛下为国着想的心胸所感动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心想助您一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么努布尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这道敕令 就是我为国着想的心灵写照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以接受了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位知道加斯塔克国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情不是太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是大陆北部边境的小国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 史特欧尔国应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梅诺利斯大陆上屈指可数的大国之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特欧尔的国力和军事力大约是我国的五倍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根据我收到的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其领土的三分之二已经被加斯塔克占领了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信 史特欧尔怎会轻易被侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是史特欧尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们究竟已经吞并了多少小国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话目前不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟距离遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 加斯塔克在地理上相距甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会成为我国的威胁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克或许不会攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 视加斯塔克为威胁的诸国
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了提升国力和军事力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必将一举挑起纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间继续国内丑陋的内讧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 弗洛瓦德有个提案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对反抗贵族设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其一举肃清的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃清？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人小孩也一起肃清吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩 那和之前的昏君有什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 克拉乌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德的提案并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这也是一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这个国家所有人的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是那些想要我命的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是罗兰德的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就应该守护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要尽力挽救他们的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不杀一人而统一国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才会采取这种强硬措施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若贵族们愿意投靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将敞开大门接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后与他们共同建设美好的罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若他们反抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有肃清一途
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让这个国家灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是否愿意与我一同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切谨遵吾王之命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切谨遵吾王之命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让贵族们尝到甜头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁其不备一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为您最终必会选择我的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要尽力挽救更多民众吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是够格的王者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您已经察觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不肯走上正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所选择的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将需要付出更多的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后您将为之烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就必须尽可能减轻您的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切谨遵陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}破忌者追击队官舍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天米拉少校还是一脸苦相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务失败他生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次失败不是我们的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是对方太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比蜜尔可队长还强的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他强的太离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连红龙都放出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个好吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定变成观光胜地了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有红龙馒头之类的土产
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是因此取消我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的破忌者我们也对付不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要救莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说要救就是要救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是这么活力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉德中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米拉少校也…呃很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个破忌者你们对付不了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这任务很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎队长别逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是取消这个任务比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我上次又没动真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我拿出真本事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一两个莱纳根本就是秒杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃这个…您说得是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然卢克都这么说了那应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后这个任务继续交由蜜尔可·卡拉德破忌者追击部队负责
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 属下当尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天要去大采购
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你们对付不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方面都超乎预想的棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩大人终于行动了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不除掉腐朽贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国就撑不下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃清什么的尽管放手去做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像比以前更憎恶贵族了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想想蜜尔可队长在卡拉德家遭到何等待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是从孤儿院收养了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉德家对军部也毫不隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说蜜尔可中尉被施以严苛的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 蜜尔可队长以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定连理所当然的幸福也未曾品尝过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在蜜尔可·卡拉德不能待在这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能让她卷入即将发生的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.96,0:11:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谁做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次次都是我做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都一定会去救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 快点发狂啊 你这恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 让他发狂真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 这不正做实验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 恶魔在挣扎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就求饶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求我圣人奇佐卡尔迪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了你这受诅咒的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去 恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊 快点发狂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底受了多久折磨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在冲出去也救不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先拟定作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是自己受伤不会发狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈因为生了个恶魔 所以死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你爸也是同罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈…妈妈因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这些人杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔亚 绝对不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能遂了他们的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我被杀了也别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非他崩溃掉成了废物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭 有敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿沉眠于大地的恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才跑过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不分男女一并通吃的禽兽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拦住他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放舞于天空的光之魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞求无处不在的神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予可怜的吾等破魔之光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不是恶魔招来了同伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对神无信仰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能篡夺神圣的卢纳魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞求无处不在的神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予可怜的吾等破魔之光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞求无处不在的神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予可怜的吾等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破魔之光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那小鬼的爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我们救不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把那边的白痴贵族打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开小鬼的绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来救我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别国的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来…给你…解开绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破魔之光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这家伙一起就能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一起 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…会救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…尔亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图释放恶魔的人 被我施以天罚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好…休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的研究材料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放下就视为恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会遭到神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说神罚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做了多么惨无人道的恶性都没受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们却只因这眼睛就要遭到神罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的增援要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 该死 该死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会遭到神罚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 为什么要创造出我们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有神灵就回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要创造我这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了肆意玩弄 再施以神罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们才不是你的玩物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…也是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不想生为这样的恶魔 这样的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是自愿长这种眼睛的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 这一切都是我们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个国家真的有神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我答案…


Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德真是个麻烦的国家啊

Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩那家伙也是 再怎么说也拼过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵族什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时抛到九霄云外
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}大扫除之宴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
